      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. but it doesn't really feel like i'm \"strong\" or anything. i just feel... empty. like there's nothing left to even try for. it's like i'm just going through the motions of a life that doesnt even belong to me anymore. everything i do feels so pointless without him there. how am i supposed to keep doing this every single day?",
